Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.42,0:00:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我就告诉你一点
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.32,0:00:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你没有自称为传说之忍的孙女的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.88,0:00:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.36,0:00:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一大早就无精打采的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.28,0:00:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城同学 一大早的你做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.17,0:00:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还在想着被蛇女那些人闯进来的事么
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.70,0:00:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}下次赢回来不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.66,0:00:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像你这样神经大条真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.04,0:00:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你说谁神经大条了？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.98,0:00:54.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你这人真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.74,0:00:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消沉下去也赢不了她们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.14,0:01:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前日的悔过书么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.12,0:01:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}至少说是报告书啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.56,0:01:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽说责任都在于我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.68,0:01:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吾师 依吾所见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.40,0:01:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前日之事乃由熟知学院之人指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:19.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不可能会有叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.46,0:01:22.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吾师亦有所察觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.02,0:01:24.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若是那个人…
Comment: 0,0:01:28.93,0:01:29.21,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,OP校准帧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:36.20,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}消えない鎖 その手で壊して
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:55.43,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}惑いに侵されて 心に潜めてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.05,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}傷だらけの　錆びた刃
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.51,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}暗雲に翳した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:05.81,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}弱さ認めぬまま 強くはなれないと
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.48,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}知った日から　目覚め出した
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.90,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}確かな熱に
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:16.07,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}螺旋の様に 絡まる紅い罠
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:23.41,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}REALを焼き付けて 彼方へ蹴散ちせ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:29.08,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}遥かな宙に　一瞬の閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.00,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}今 亂れ咲き　影を纏い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.38,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}朧雲に放て
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.91,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}信じる道は
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:42.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}必ずこの手で切り拓くと誓い立てて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:47.56,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}見えない鎖 撃ち抜けmaze
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.76,0:02:50.34,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}You DON'T need to grieve anymore
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.34,0:02:52.95,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Who can read the future? Know thyself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.95,0:02:55.39,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Ready now！ Discern truth or false
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.39,0:02:57.35,OP-JP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}Break your world
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.44,0:01:36.20,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}几重枷锁 手中破
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:55.43,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}困惑侵扰 心中隐匿
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.43,0:01:58.05,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}斑驳疮痍 刀刃发锈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.05,0:02:00.51,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}却为暗云罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:05.81,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}不堪羸弱 誓要更强
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.81,0:02:08.48,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}自知起 更醒悟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.48,0:02:10.90,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}热忱之切实
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:16.07,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}庞若螺旋 赤罠笼络
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:23.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}铭刻现实 掷向彼方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:29.08,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}远空迢遥 一瞬閃光
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.21,0:02:32.00,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}绮丽绽放 犹纏暗影
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.38,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}耀于朧云上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.51,0:02:36.91,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}所坚信
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.99,0:02:42.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}誓以我手 开辟我路
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:47.56,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,250)\blur2}击穿那道 无形枷锁
