Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.20,0:03:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不喜欢这修行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.92,0:03:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}比起其他的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这已经很轻松了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.20,0:03:11.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但人家花了两小时整理的头发都泡汤了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.30,0:03:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谁管你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们有听说么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.30,0:03:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我还什么都没说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.01,0:03:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}反正就是豆芽菜的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.08,0:03:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那请务必与我畅谈一番
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.60,0:03:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果还不是想说么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.56,0:03:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说铃音老师好像曾经是善忍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那只不过是传闻而已吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.98,0:03:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}善忍怎么可能会成为蛇女的教官
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.42,0:03:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可不好说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}未来 你想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.68,0:03:40.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这话也不能说死了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.32,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}焰你不也是善忍家系出身么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.68,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}住嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.78,0:03:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我家原本也是善忍的家系
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你敢再多嘴一句
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.18,0:03:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟然说铃音老师是善忍？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.96,0:04:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}陷阱？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟要无故设计陷害老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.74,0:04:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}令我十分心痛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.41,0:04:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但这是主人亲自下达的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.72,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我无法拒绝
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.27,0:04:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然还没有得到完全信任么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但为何将此事告知于我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是你和那男人的密约么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.99,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}因为我是老师的学生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:27.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而且对我来说多增加几个人偶也无妨
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.96,0:04:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你依旧是个令人难以捉摸的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.28,0:04:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没有这回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不过是单纯罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只要能从中享乐即可
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.42,0:04:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}先谢你一声
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.13,0:04:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说起来 您教我的连锁结界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.38,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说那是老师于学生时代所创
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.08,0:04:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那么厉害的忍术
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.66,0:04:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没落入半藏学院真是万幸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.24,0:04:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.34,0:04:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}连锁结界啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.38,0:05:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然这忍法有难度过高的缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.08,0:05:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但由学生开发出新忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.39,0:05:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是前所未闻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我的目标是成为超级忍者嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.54,0:05:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这种程度是理所当然的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.61,0:05:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是我的骄傲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.56,0:05:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}做得好 凛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.61,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.02,0:05:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}凛已经死了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.14,0:05:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在那次任务失败时就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.81,0:05:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}殒命于任务乃忍之荣耀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.08,0:05:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}然 吾睹其骨前仍不敢信
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}而后 吾终寻到…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.96,0:05:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}找到什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其装束寄宿着恶忍之气
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.70,0:05:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}恶忍之气？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.16,0:05:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}乃吾曾遇恶忍所不可比拟之恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.02,0:05:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.88,0:05:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那时候出现的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.58,0:05:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}若是吾师
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.80,0:06:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不 正是吾师才更应发觉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.15,0:06:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}蛇女学园那些女孩的招式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.04,0:06:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正乃其无数忍术之应用
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我只看过报告书
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并未亲眼目睹过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所以说…是为了不让我发觉而故意隐藏起来了么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可有觉悟 吾师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吾师有将学子卷入此场战斗的觉悟么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.60,0:06:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要爬这座山么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.64,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这与其说是开开心心的远足
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.38,0:06:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}{\fs36\pos(654,650)}hiking
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.62,0:06:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不如说是危险的秘境探险
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.88,0:06:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这么说确实相像啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}相像？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.40,0:06:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.64,0:06:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那被称为禁忌修行的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.62,0:06:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是斑鸠
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.22,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果 果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.72,0:06:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.18,0:06:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}数年前曾举行过一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但之后因为过于危险而成为禁忌的修行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.58,0:06:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其名亦为
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这紧虞
