Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.12,0:06:59.38,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\an7}注：与hiking同音
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这紧虞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.42,0:07:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}其主旨为增强生存之术
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在最低限度的装备下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}于极限环境中生存两天
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.68,0:07:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}并且还要同时完成任务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.92,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是对于忍者而言最为严酷的修行之一
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这…这不是我想的那个远足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(848,650)}hiking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.68,0:07:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}和云雀想的也不一样！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.00,0:07:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在这座山顶放有某个卷轴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.38,0:07:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}能拿到那个卷轴之人就是胜利者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也就是说每个人都是竞争对手
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这倒有点意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀还是觉得普通的远足比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs30\pos(765,650)}hiking
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放心吧 云雀就由俺来守护
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要加油了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.58,0:07:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.14,0:07:42.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}纵使尚未明了彼等意图
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.86,0:07:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但其目标无疑是此五人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.68,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽应予五人特性以赞许
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.00,0:07:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但五人成长之不具
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.06,0:07:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}症结正为吾师之踌躇
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:05.67,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(881,559)\fad(700,700)\bord2\blur5\1a&HFF}恐怖的远足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.37,0:08:05.67,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(880,558)\fad(700,700)\c&HE3EFED&}恐怖的远足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一开始就是个难关啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.26,0:08:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好…好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord5}忍法 鼯鼠滑翔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.20,0:08:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍法 鼯鼠滑翔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.78,0:08:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是利用由特殊纤维制成的幕布滑翔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.56,0:08:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由高处向地面飞行的空中移动术之一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.16,0:08:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}着陆…失败…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.36,0:08:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.57,0:08:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}前路漫漫呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.86,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在一天之内是不可能登顶的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}体力的分配可是攸关性命的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}目标！第一名！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.20,0:08:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}夜间要注重休息
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.48,0:08:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.62,0:08:53.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这也是训练的一环
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.56,0:08:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总之要先和云雀会合呐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.20,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里真的是日本么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.92,0:09:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好冷…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.24,0:09:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里真的是日本么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.38,0:09:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚才差点被风刮走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.76,0:09:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀应该是在这一带吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}糟糕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.80,0:09:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这缔魔破空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.34,0:09:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可不只是一座普通的山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但我相信你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.28,0:09:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}定能克服艰险直到最后
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.98,0:09:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}缔魔破空
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.00,0:09:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即为设有无数能陷人于极限状况的陷阱
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.32,0:09:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}用来进行修行的特殊空间
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.30,0:10:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这条蛇为何散发出如此邪恶下流的气息
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鳗鱼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.14,0:10:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不…不对
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有胡须的话应该是泥鳅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.58,0:10:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不是说这话的时候啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.98,0:10:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}既然到这份上了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.68,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对不起啊 泥鳅先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.60,0:10:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那…那里是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.22,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还不认输么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:47.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}熊：认输了（咦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}区区一头熊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.22,0:10:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也敢小看我半藏学院首席打手 葛城么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}总之不先变件暖和的衣服出来可会得感冒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.12,0:11:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}算了 反正暖和就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.90,0:11:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嘿哟 嘿哟冲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.56,0:11:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}把武器当作落脚点真是个错误的选择
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样就没法反击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.25,0:11:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.22,0:11:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.78,0:11:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}鱼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.96,0:11:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这些是食人鱼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.38,0:11:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}食人鱼先生？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.62,0:11:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀 别管我了快走
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.96,0:11:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.62,0:11:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我会救小柳生的！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.64,0:11:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.00,0:11:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord5}秘传忍法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord5}“忍兔BOOM”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.64,0:11:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}兔子先生谢谢你～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生 没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.88,0:11:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只伤到了衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}本以为河川是最安全的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.24,0:12:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}结果也不尽然呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.98,0:12:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}云雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.75,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.08,0:12:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.56,0:12:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.42,0:12:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胸…胸那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.74,0:12:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}哼 大意了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}得赶紧了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.96,0:12:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}在天亮前就露宿在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.68,0:12:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}来者何人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}等等 是咱家啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.14,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城同学么？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.62,0:12:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.68,0:12:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出了这样的事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.92,0:12:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这里比想像的还乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那也是修行的一环呐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.84,0:12:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肚子饿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.60,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真是的 连食物都没确保么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.26,0:12:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拿去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.42,0:13:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是橡实么！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.14,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}顺路收集的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.60,0:13:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是…这样好么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.40,0:13:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}请吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.28,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真不愧是班长
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.84,0:13:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一般人可做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.36,0:13:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这样给敌人雪中抹炭的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那话怎么说也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.04,0:13:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“雪中送炭”吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不要在意细节啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那我不客气咯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.14,0:13:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.14,0:13:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这前头还有一眼温泉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.36,0:13:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}温泉！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.56,0:13:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不知道大家是否安康
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.14,0:13:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她们会有办法的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.46,0:13:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.68,0:13:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}想起了些旧事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.74,0:13:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}以前？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚入学那时
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也只有我们俩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}啊 是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.78,0:13:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真怀念呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.32,0:13:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}好厉害！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.84,0:14:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}涌泉水池呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.24,0:14:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}多少能洗去身上的汗水
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.34,0:14:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}毕竟河川太危险了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.00,0:14:10.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}会被食人鱼先生们关照呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.58,0:14:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}刚才真的很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.37,0:14:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.16,0:14:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}光想着要云雀逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.42,0:14:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全没想到云雀要来救俺
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺没能信任云雀…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不会哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我也没想到能帮上小柳生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.26,0:14:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但是在我细想之前 身体就先一步行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.12,0:14:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生总是想得太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:36.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这点我倒是得承认呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.44,0:14:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只有我一个人的感觉真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你没有自称为传说之忍的孙女的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.44,0:14:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从这里爬上去就是顶峰了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.32,0:15:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱家才不会输呐！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.22,0:15:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}从这里穿过去应该是条近路才对
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:10.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不过还是好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.18,0:15:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}希望别冒出什么东西来
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.50,0:15:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可不能为这点小事就害怕！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.54,0:15:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我可是传说之忍的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.90,0:15:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.36,0:15:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是谁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.38,0:15:23.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}传说之忍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.08,0:15:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}纵为其孙女又有何价值
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.00,0:15:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}出现啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血脉不过是缘之记录
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}受其摆布实属愚蠢之极
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.14,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我才没有受摆布！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}血缘能使汝变强么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那汝“自身”又是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.22,0:15:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}“自身”？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我自己…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.98,0:15:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.36,0:16:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不行了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.28,0:16:10.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你没有自称为传说之忍的孙女的资格
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.26,0:16:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}果然我根本没资格…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.60,0:16:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你很像你爸爸呐
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.72,0:16:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}像爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.26,0:16:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.78,0:16:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你的爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.30,0:16:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}面对坚决反对他和你妈妈结婚的我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.14,0:16:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}放弃了成为律师的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要开寿司店
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.34,0:16:31.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}说是“为了要和相爱之人白头偕老
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.46,0:16:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}不论是梦想 还是金钱、地位都可以放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.88,0:16:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}现在的自己有的就是这份觉悟”
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.50,0:16:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只靠这份觉悟就说服了我半藏啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.32,0:16:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你爸爸可真是个不可貌相的强者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.96,0:16:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}还有你那位对他一见钟情的妈妈也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.32,0:16:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}没什么资不资格的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.06,0:16:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有爷爷在
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.22,0:17:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}有爸爸妈妈在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}才有了现在的我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.84,0:17:03.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我要明白的就这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur10\bord5}秘传忍法“二刀缭斩”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由期待而生的压力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.06,0:17:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}由压力而生的自卑感
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这亦为
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}内心狭隘的阴霾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.88,0:17:22.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}区区阴霾不足为惧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.27,0:17:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.23,0:17:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}铭记于心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.24,0:17:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}真正的恐怖便是汝自身之弱小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.16,0:17:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}穿过这片丛林
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.34,0:17:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}应该就是一路通往山顶了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.20,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽说只是我的直觉啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}俺相信云雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.06,0:17:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}同时到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}胜负如何呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}头奖该怎么算呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.62,0:17:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是谁！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.66,0:17:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吾从不自己现身
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所求若为胜者之证
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.26,0:18:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便尽汝等所能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.69,0:18:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.92,0:18:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吾乃缔魔破空最后一关
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}亦为这紧虞之目标
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.56,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs36\pos(620,650)}hiking
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}卷轴…那就是要打败这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}让我们抢的意思么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.90,0:18:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.32,0:18:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}吾即大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你是大道寺！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.16,0:18:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}难道你就是传说中的…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大道寺学姐！？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.96,0:18:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你们知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.42,0:18:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只听说过名字
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.84,0:18:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽然早早就能通过毕业测试
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.32,0:18:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}却执意留级多年的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.80,0:18:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}传说中的超强学姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.43,0:18:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}竟…竟然有这种人存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.12,0:18:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}留级了好几年
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}只凭这个就足以被称为传说了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.60,0:18:42.85,Comment,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大道寺学姐可是25岁的现役高中生！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.85,0:18:44.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}话说回来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}原来是女的么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}感觉好有男子汉气概啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.10,0:18:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}一个个上连准备活动都称不上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.86,0:18:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}汝等一起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.54,0:19:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可笑至极
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这力量…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}完全不在一个档次上
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.84,0:19:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}咱们都到这儿了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.98,0:19:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}怎么能甘心放弃！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}肤浅
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.94,0:19:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者之名都在哭泣了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.34,0:19:30.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}大家的攻击竟然一点也不奏效
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这不是凭我能战胜的对手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.26,0:19:35.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}可是！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.96,0:19:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}要是逃走了就输给自己了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}飞鸟同学！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.76,0:19:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小飞鸟 振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.20,0:19:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}忍者学科的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.56,0:19:58.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也真是堕落了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.57,0:20:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就到此为止吧 大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.06,0:20:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}雾夜老师
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.18,0:20:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是怎么一回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}企划了这次这紧虞的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.30,0:20:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fs36\pos(722,650)}hiking
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.40,0:20:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}正是这位大道寺
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.12,0:20:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}她说希望能为学妹们的修行出一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.96,0:20:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}传说中的学姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.48,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}为什么会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.99,0:20:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那一击虽尚显稚嫩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.28,0:20:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}却有一瞬还吾以颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.54,0:20:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}此举有其价值所在
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}就是说飞鸟胜出了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.94,0:20:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}也没办法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.10,0:20:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.06,0:20:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拥有相当的潜力
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.04,0:20:50.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}虽说她自身尚未意识到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.58,0:20:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你果然也发现了么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.61,0:20:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}潜藏的强大即为无意中的强大
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.58,0:20:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}故为双刃之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.16,0:21:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}但若走错一步
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.82,0:21:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}便会重蹈那个人的覆辙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.44,0:21:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我再也不会让那种事发生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.64,0:21:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}老师 我要成为超级忍者！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.21,0:21:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}上面写着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.78,0:21:17.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}快点打开看看啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}葛城同学 真不像话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.67,0:21:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}你不也想知道么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.48,0:21:24.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那个 确实…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.16,0:21:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}写着什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.84,0:21:32.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}力即刀盾
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.14,0:21:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}此为半藏大人亲书的忍之极意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}所谓的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.74,0:21:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}即是刀与盾缺一不可
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.78,0:21:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我不会再说丧气话了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.66,0:21:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}爷爷 我会加油的！
Comment: 0,0:21:53.02,0:21:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,ED3
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:22:03.00,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}それでいい　不連続な願望が心を導くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:08.70,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}走り続けて行くだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:26.06,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}はじめは　何も見えていない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:31.68,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}輝く意味すら分からない
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:37.32,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}地中に埋もれた石のように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:42.30,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}目を閉じ　夜明けを忍んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:46.20,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}ひりひりするような思いが
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:50.99,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}息を殺しながら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:54.45,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}舞い上がる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:23:00.56,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}私は走り続けてるから私だ　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:05.82,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}今日も明日も止まらない時の先へ　
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:12.56,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}それでいい　不連続な願望が心を導くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:16.70,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}恐れなんて打ちのめして
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:22.46,ED3-JP,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}夢を走り続けていくだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.56,0:22:03.00,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}这样便好 若是断续的愿望能指引我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.00,0:22:08.70,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}任我奔跑到底
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.34,0:22:26.06,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}最初 什么也看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.06,0:22:31.68,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}甚至连閃耀的意义都不曾知晓
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.68,0:22:37.32,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}庞若地里埋藏的石头
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.35,0:22:42.30,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}闭上眼 直待天明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.30,0:22:46.20,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}回忆刺痛着我的神经
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.20,0:22:50.99,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}屏住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:54.45,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}飞舞而上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.45,0:23:00.56,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}我奔跑故有我在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.56,0:23:05.82,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}不论今日明日都奔向那止不住的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.82,0:23:12.56,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}这样便好 若是断续的愿望能指引我的内心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.56,0:23:16.70,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}击败自身的恐惧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.70,0:23:22.46,ED3-CH,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,200)}向着梦想奔跑到底
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.40,0:23:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}听说斑鸠同学和葛城姐以前关系不好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.46,0:23:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}这是真的么
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.66,0:23:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}是啊 那可是相当差
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.43,0:23:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}我刚来的时候呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.32,0:23:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可是相当新
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.93,0:23:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}小柳生和小云雀呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.44,0:23:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}那可是相当要好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}次回 追忆的忍者教室
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur5}拼上性命来相夺吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:39.97,Chapter,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,484)\bord2\blur2\shad1\c&HE2EEEE&\3c&H383A3B&}追忆的忍者教室
